Wash and dry @mixed greens{2%ounce}.

Halve @ciabatta bread{2}. Toast in a #toaster{} or #pan{} until golden, if desired.

In a #medium bowl{}, toss mixed greens with a large drizzle of @olive oil{2%teaspoon} and @balsamic vinegar{25%milliliters} to taste. Season with @salt{} and @pepper{}.

Spread @fig jam{2%ounce} onto cut sides of ciabatta. Fill with @prosciutto{2%ounce}, @gouda cheese{4%slice}, and a small handful of leaves from salad.

Cut sandwiches on a diagonal, if desired. Serve with remaining salad on the side.